  {
    "id": "f_csv_e148d66ffe",
    "slug": "everyday-i-realize-more-and-more-that-if-the-world-is-going-to-change-at-all-it",
    "texto": "Everyday I realize more and more that if the world is going to change at all, it is going to change through the healing of the victims. Abusers run the show, they insist on and instigate cover ups, they misuse their power, teach things falsely out of the desire to control but as the victims heal and get stronger, the abusers will not be able to hide behind the fog that they create.",
